I"ò<p>This lesson assumes you have R and RStudio installed on your computer.</p>

<p>The latest version of R can be downloaded <a href="https://cran.r-project.org/mirrors.html">here</a>.</p>

<p>RStudio is an application (an integrated development environment or IDE) that facilitates the use of R and offers a number of nice additional features.
It can be downloaded <a href="https://www.rstudio.com/products/rstudio/download/">here</a>.
You will need the free Desktop version for your computer.</p>
